WEBVTT

01:35.900 --> 01:40.980
=Love Beyond the Grave=
(Adapted from the novel by Li Qingran)

01:41.260 --> 01:43.990
=Episode 30=

01:56.990 --> 01:57.830
Simu.

02:13.420 --> 02:14.260
Simu,

02:16.350 --> 02:17.790
based on what I saw

02:17.790 --> 02:18.950
in your father's illusion,

02:19.510 --> 02:20.350
I built this place.

02:22.740 --> 02:24.350
It carries the memories of your family

02:25.020 --> 02:26.420
in the Mortal World.

02:28.300 --> 02:29.580
I want you to see a lively world

02:30.950 --> 02:32.110
full of colors.

02:34.270 --> 02:35.110
I believe

02:35.120 --> 02:36.230
you love this world.

02:40.300 --> 02:41.700
If only you could

02:44.270 --> 02:45.140
love me a little more.

02:59.990 --> 03:01.300
If I hadn't come today,

03:01.830 --> 03:02.950
what would you do?

03:04.180 --> 03:05.460
If you lost this bet,

03:06.390 --> 03:07.700
what would you bet with next time?

03:07.700 --> 03:08.860
I have no more chips.

03:10.900 --> 03:12.020
It's a desperate bet

03:13.420 --> 03:14.460
on your compassion

03:16.300 --> 03:17.350
and on you falling for me.

03:21.580 --> 03:22.790
I bet that you'd come to me.

03:43.110 --> 03:44.020
I don't know

03:44.550 --> 03:45.950
what you want from all this.

04:04.070 --> 04:05.390
I want to be with you.

04:09.180 --> 04:10.620
I once told you.

04:12.110 --> 04:13.830
I'm a wish you can't fulfill.

04:15.620 --> 04:16.480
Even so,

04:16.480 --> 04:17.990
will you persist without turning back?

04:18.710 --> 04:19.550
Simu,

04:21.260 --> 04:22.590
I love being with you.

04:24.550 --> 04:25.390
Your Grace,

04:26.500 --> 04:27.470
I adore you.

04:32.110 --> 04:33.910
I wonder if I have the honor

04:36.820 --> 04:37.910
to be the 23rd grave

04:37.910 --> 04:39.550
behind the Void Mountain.

05:10.110 --> 05:10.950
All right.

05:11.940 --> 05:12.780
I accept.

05:19.060 --> 05:19.940
I accept you.

05:24.350 --> 05:25.910
You're so cunning.

05:28.110 --> 05:29.990
You want the Sovereign as a gift.

05:30.860 --> 05:37.180
♪Light the lamps
to pierce the old night♪

05:41.760 --> 05:48.910
♪Borrow mortal warmth to ease the cold♪

05:49.110 --> 05:55.880
♪Warm winds bring fragrant blooms♪

05:55.910 --> 05:56.750
Simu,

05:57.940 --> 05:59.350
I have a blessed flower.

06:02.260 --> 06:03.550
Fengyi is really generous.

06:05.740 --> 06:07.470
Let me give you my sense of touch.

06:09.420 --> 06:10.940
I want you to remember me.

06:12.010 --> 06:14.630
♪With you by my side♪

06:18.420 --> 06:19.260
All right.

06:19.990 --> 06:20.830
Whatever you say.

06:29.040 --> 06:33.020
♪Falling into your gentle smile♪

06:34.590 --> 06:40.750
♪Light and color are there in your eyes♪

06:43.640 --> 06:48.260
♪If you'd let me know how to tell♪

06:49.000 --> 06:56.970
♪The difference between spring
and autumn, love and worry♪

06:58.110 --> 07:05.230
♪Borrow mortal warmth to ease the cold♪

07:05.520 --> 07:12.520
♪Warm winds bring fragrant blooms♪

07:12.730 --> 07:19.870
♪Let me love with all my heart
in youthful grace♪

07:19.980 --> 07:28.890
♪With light, carefree words,
still shining bright♪

07:29.550 --> 07:34.720
♪A pot of wine in fleeting dreams♪

07:36.310 --> 07:40.120
♪A brief life dares seek eternity♪

07:40.150 --> 07:40.990
What...

07:41.790 --> 07:42.860
What is this feeling?

07:44.820 --> 07:46.150
I feel as if a gust of strong wind

07:46.150 --> 07:47.350
is flying out

07:48.990 --> 07:50.550
from my heart.

07:52.770 --> 07:55.640
♪May I roam drunk in dreams♪

07:55.710 --> 07:56.670
You're falling for me.

07:56.670 --> 07:59.360
♪And never forget♪

07:59.710 --> 08:00.670
I'm so delighted.

08:01.860 --> 08:03.230
This is like a dream.

08:04.090 --> 08:07.330
♪Through this life♪

08:08.620 --> 08:10.500
I've never had such a sweet dream.

08:10.890 --> 08:17.070
♪I see a ray♪

08:19.370 --> 08:22.070
♪To what home shall I return♪

08:44.900 --> 08:47.900
(Virtue of the Land)

08:50.430 --> 08:52.190
Don't you know who those guests are?

08:53.140 --> 08:54.620
You made a serious pledge there.

08:55.620 --> 08:56.740
Did your trip to the border

08:56.740 --> 08:57.580
make you so arrogant

08:57.580 --> 08:58.710
that you thought you could

08:58.710 --> 08:59.620
confront Chong troops?

09:04.660 --> 09:05.900
They insulted me like that.

09:06.710 --> 09:07.950
I was just so angry

09:09.380 --> 09:10.620
that I made a big boast.

09:13.110 --> 09:14.310
Now, Qin Huanda

09:14.590 --> 09:15.430
has lost his power.

09:16.190 --> 09:17.710
Duke Pei's influence within the army

09:17.710 --> 09:18.660
is severely crippled.

09:19.620 --> 09:20.830
Chancellor Du wants to build up

09:20.830 --> 09:21.900
his military strength.

09:22.740 --> 09:23.860
I don't actually want this.

09:25.070 --> 09:25.910
But indeed,

09:27.540 --> 09:29.190
you're the best choice.

09:30.380 --> 09:31.430
You will probably

09:31.430 --> 09:32.350
stay in the army.

09:33.710 --> 09:35.140
The heroic boast you made yesterday

09:35.400 --> 09:36.260
would go around town

09:36.260 --> 09:37.350
within just one day.

09:38.590 --> 09:39.710
Once His Majesty hears it,

09:40.950 --> 09:42.470
he will definitely reward you.

09:43.710 --> 09:44.710
I guess

09:45.860 --> 09:47.540
that's the only benefit.

09:55.830 --> 09:57.140
Whatever you decide, Father.

10:56.780 --> 10:58.190
I thought you would be gone

10:59.380 --> 11:00.220
when I came back.

11:03.020 --> 11:04.110
You and Fengyi teamed up

11:04.110 --> 11:05.350
to rid me of my power.

11:05.660 --> 11:06.620
Where else could I go?

11:11.860 --> 11:13.260
What's the color of an orange?

11:13.620 --> 11:14.460
Orange.

11:16.620 --> 11:18.190
The color of an orange is just orange?

11:19.620 --> 11:20.540
What about that?

11:20.540 --> 11:21.380
Grape?

11:22.830 --> 11:24.860
Oh, that one. That's...

11:26.710 --> 11:27.550
Purple.

11:30.740 --> 11:31.580
What about this?

11:34.540 --> 11:35.380
Who slapped you?

11:36.780 --> 11:37.620
It's all right.

11:38.620 --> 11:39.830
I have no sense of touch now.

11:40.540 --> 11:41.380
I can't feel pain.

11:42.430 --> 11:43.380
Was it your father?

11:46.310 --> 11:47.780
He didn't save your life back then.

11:48.140 --> 11:49.590
How did he have the face to slap you?

11:53.500 --> 11:54.950
My father wouldn't think

11:55.380 --> 11:56.350
he did anything wrong.

11:59.260 --> 12:00.140
Do you remember

12:00.140 --> 12:01.310
the Tianluo Ore

12:02.310 --> 12:03.190
I once told

12:03.590 --> 12:04.430
those generals?

12:06.950 --> 12:07.790
Yes.

12:09.740 --> 12:10.900
Wensheng Agency was

12:10.900 --> 12:12.260
the spy outpost my father set up.

12:13.190 --> 12:14.190
Its director,

12:14.190 --> 12:15.190
serving under my father,

12:15.500 --> 12:16.830
knew the purification of that ore.

12:18.860 --> 12:19.900
Chong soldiers abducted me

12:20.620 --> 12:21.780
and threatened my father

12:22.310 --> 12:23.540
to tell them that method.

12:24.950 --> 12:25.790
But my father

12:27.020 --> 12:28.140
ultimately didn't yield.

12:31.590 --> 12:32.430
What do you think?

12:33.230 --> 12:34.780
When my father was young,

12:35.310 --> 12:36.660
he was a great hero, wasn't he?

12:41.310 --> 12:42.540
How could I blame him

12:44.260 --> 12:45.780
for giving up on me

12:47.310 --> 12:48.190
to defend this nation

12:48.190 --> 12:49.350
and protect a national secret

12:50.950 --> 12:51.830
from our enemies?

12:56.110 --> 12:57.380
But he's old after all.

12:59.740 --> 13:00.990
That director's daughter

13:02.140 --> 13:03.540
is Luoxian at Yuzao Pleasure House.

13:04.590 --> 13:05.430
Now,

13:05.620 --> 13:06.660
she's in charge.

13:07.950 --> 13:09.020
My father always thinks

13:09.020 --> 13:09.990
Luoxian is loyal to him.

13:10.830 --> 13:11.740
But actually,

13:13.110 --> 13:14.380
she has long been my subordinate.

13:16.020 --> 13:17.380
Whatever he learns from Luoxian

13:18.380 --> 13:19.710
is what I want him to know.

13:40.860 --> 13:41.990
Are you upset about it?

13:48.020 --> 13:49.070
With no expectations,

13:50.900 --> 13:51.950
nothing can upset me.

14:01.430 --> 14:02.290
Maybe before,

14:02.290 --> 14:03.430
you never relied on anyone.

14:04.380 --> 14:05.900
But you can rely on me from now on.

14:09.830 --> 14:11.070
Because you're mine.

14:12.540 --> 14:13.950
I never make promises casually.

14:15.350 --> 14:16.190
But once I make one,

14:16.190 --> 14:17.540
I'll always keep it.

14:18.660 --> 14:19.660
You can trust me.

14:26.190 --> 14:27.030
I can?

14:28.500 --> 14:30.260
From now on, I'm your family too.

14:59.830 --> 15:00.670
High Priest,

15:01.230 --> 15:02.070
I'm so sorry.

15:03.350 --> 15:04.860
To make my life smooth,

15:05.430 --> 15:06.500
my father was bewitched

15:06.740 --> 15:07.590
and did wrong things.

15:08.140 --> 15:09.230
He atoned for his sins.

15:09.620 --> 15:11.190
But everything happened because of me.

15:11.470 --> 15:12.710
I'll take my punishment.

15:15.020 --> 15:16.070
Your father

15:16.070 --> 15:18.070
actively made a pact with an evil spirit

15:18.430 --> 15:20.590
in exchange for the wealth and glory

15:20.590 --> 15:22.070
of your clan.

15:24.380 --> 15:25.220
Please see the truth.

15:26.020 --> 15:27.580
My father was really bewitched

15:28.070 --> 15:29.070
to take the wrong path.

15:29.310 --> 15:30.150
Guards!

15:31.830 --> 15:32.670
Move!

15:34.900 --> 15:35.740
Father.

15:36.620 --> 15:37.780
Father. Father.

15:40.690 --> 15:41.540
- High Priest.
- Luda.

15:41.540 --> 15:42.380
I...

15:43.540 --> 15:46.740
You're the disciple I care about most.

15:48.260 --> 15:49.350
If people get to know

15:50.230 --> 15:51.990
that your father had a pact

15:52.190 --> 15:53.430
with an evil spirit,

15:54.710 --> 15:56.110
how will they

15:57.310 --> 15:59.190
trust us anymore?

16:05.740 --> 16:06.580
Here.

16:08.620 --> 16:10.230
Execute Yili'er.

16:13.140 --> 16:14.430
Then you'll only be stripped

16:14.430 --> 16:15.780
of your position.

16:29.310 --> 16:30.230
Luda.

17:10.670 --> 17:11.510
High Priest,

17:13.910 --> 17:15.910
I'll give up my position

17:16.580 --> 17:17.470
to atone for my father.

17:23.300 --> 17:24.140
You...

17:49.820 --> 17:50.660
Mentor!

17:51.100 --> 17:51.940
Mentor.

17:53.470 --> 17:54.710
Mentor. Mentor.

17:56.870 --> 17:57.710
Mentor.

17:58.340 --> 17:59.180
Mentor.

18:06.780 --> 18:07.620
Father!

18:09.990 --> 18:11.300
Father, Father.

18:12.340 --> 18:13.180
Father.

18:17.670 --> 18:19.500
Be the High Priest.

18:20.190 --> 18:22.820
You must be the High Priest

18:22.990 --> 18:29.230
to bring honor to our clan.

18:30.340 --> 18:32.020
Father. Father!

18:32.190 --> 18:33.100
Wake up.

18:33.100 --> 18:34.390
Don't scare me, Father.

18:34.990 --> 18:35.830
Father.

18:36.470 --> 18:37.780
Father, wake up.

18:38.150 --> 18:40.300
I beg you. Don't scare me.

18:46.470 --> 18:48.710
For your family's honor,

18:49.230 --> 18:50.540
your father even died

18:50.540 --> 18:51.580
with your mentor.

18:53.780 --> 18:56.150
Now, you're no longer the Young Priest.

18:59.870 --> 19:00.710
Luda,

19:01.670 --> 19:03.020
are you reconciled to this?

19:09.630 --> 19:10.470
The world is vast.

19:10.950 --> 19:12.020
Living beings are small.

19:13.150 --> 19:14.020
This is karma.

19:14.580 --> 19:15.780
Yet it might be reversed.

19:16.540 --> 19:17.580
Have mercy upon us.

19:17.820 --> 19:18.990
When you cover your ears,

19:18.990 --> 19:21.300
you just can't hear the mortals.

19:22.470 --> 19:23.310
I'm different.

19:24.190 --> 19:25.500
Your heart is unsettled.

19:25.710 --> 19:27.910
Even Cangshen can't protect you.

19:30.390 --> 19:31.580
But I can.

19:32.340 --> 19:33.180
What do you say?

19:33.780 --> 19:35.340
How dare you come to me

19:35.500 --> 19:36.910
after my father died because of you?

19:38.710 --> 19:40.430
Because we're of the same kind.

19:41.100 --> 19:42.780
Your obsession and desire

19:42.910 --> 19:44.470
have drawn me here.

19:47.910 --> 19:49.150
I can get you out

19:49.150 --> 19:50.340
of today's predicament

19:51.500 --> 19:54.340
and make you the High Priest.

20:04.100 --> 20:06.870
I'd rather die
than go along with evil spirits.

20:09.190 --> 20:10.870
He won't let you go

20:11.150 --> 20:12.740
unless he's dead.

20:15.150 --> 20:16.910
I'll wait for you to come find me.

20:50.190 --> 20:51.430
The world is vast.

20:51.910 --> 20:53.230
Living beings are small.

20:53.780 --> 20:54.870
This is karma.

20:55.500 --> 20:56.740
Yet it might be reversed.

21:26.150 --> 21:26.990
Xiaoxiao.

21:27.230 --> 21:28.710
Xiaoxiao, I missed you so much!

21:29.190 --> 21:30.540
Xu said he would bring me to you.

21:30.540 --> 21:31.380
Then here I am.

21:31.540 --> 21:32.380
Jingyuan.

21:32.540 --> 21:33.380
Look around.

21:33.630 --> 21:35.390
I've been doing everything Xu tells me.

21:35.670 --> 21:36.910
I take classes

21:37.060 --> 21:38.020
and do martial arts.

21:38.580 --> 21:40.540
Now I'm really good at martial arts.

21:40.620 --> 21:41.500
I can help you

21:41.500 --> 21:42.340
fight bad people.

21:43.540 --> 21:44.380
Xiaoxiao,

21:44.710 --> 21:46.060
how long will you stay this time?

21:46.230 --> 21:47.500
Will you stay forever with us?

21:51.500 --> 21:52.670
I'll stay for some days.

21:53.950 --> 21:54.910
That's great.

21:54.910 --> 21:56.190
You, Xu,

21:56.190 --> 21:57.030
and I

21:57.030 --> 21:58.150
can be together again.

22:03.020 --> 22:03.910
You are the one

22:03.910 --> 22:04.820
I met

22:04.820 --> 22:05.660
at Yueran Fragrance.

22:09.870 --> 22:10.710
Jingyuan.

22:11.430 --> 22:12.630
This is the girl I love,

22:12.950 --> 22:13.790
He Simu.

22:40.710 --> 22:41.950
So,

22:43.100 --> 22:45.430
Miss Wang wasn't abducted.

22:46.630 --> 22:47.870
You planned all that.

22:48.340 --> 22:49.710
She eloped with her sweetheart?

22:52.740 --> 22:53.780
I helped them

22:54.060 --> 22:54.990
and appeased Father.

22:55.670 --> 22:56.780
I also stayed true

22:56.780 --> 22:57.620
to my own love.

22:59.230 --> 23:00.070
Triple win.

23:03.060 --> 23:03.900
But Xu,

23:04.390 --> 23:05.580
you just made that oath.

23:05.580 --> 23:06.910
How will you marry Miss He?

23:08.870 --> 23:10.060
She's from the martial world.

23:10.580 --> 23:11.670
Single heir for generations.

23:12.340 --> 23:13.260
To be with her,

23:13.740 --> 23:14.780
I must join her family.

23:20.700 --> 23:21.540
If Father finds out,

23:21.540 --> 23:22.670
he'll break your legs.

23:24.870 --> 23:25.820
So Xu,

23:26.100 --> 23:27.340
you and Xiaoxiao

23:27.740 --> 23:28.990
are secretly betrothed?

23:32.230 --> 23:33.070
Chenying,

23:33.540 --> 23:34.540
it's been a long time.

23:35.300 --> 23:36.820
Shall I quiz you on your schoolwork?

23:42.630 --> 23:43.540
Well,

23:44.230 --> 23:46.100
let's change the subject.

23:51.740 --> 23:53.390
Look, what a beautiful windmill.

24:24.430 --> 24:25.630
I've always wanted to know

24:26.470 --> 24:27.870
what I look like in your paintings.

24:29.390 --> 24:30.500
The first time I saw you,

24:31.390 --> 24:32.260
I thought you were

24:32.260 --> 24:33.710
a dazzling young man.

24:34.820 --> 24:35.660
And then?

24:40.990 --> 24:42.950
When I saw the wounds on you,

24:43.470 --> 24:44.470
I thought...

24:47.390 --> 24:49.260
You were like porcelain
with ice crackles.

24:50.230 --> 24:51.150
So I look really good

24:51.150 --> 24:51.990
in your eyes.

24:54.020 --> 24:55.390
Aren't you very afraid of pain?

24:57.710 --> 24:59.020
I'm very sensitive to pain.

24:59.500 --> 25:00.390
But I'm not afraid.

25:01.670 --> 25:02.870
I yelled about pain

25:05.540 --> 25:06.870
just to make you care about me.

25:30.230 --> 25:31.100
To me,

25:31.580 --> 25:32.870
this is what a family is.

25:37.950 --> 25:38.990
Hey, don't smudge it.

25:40.990 --> 25:42.500
Then paint another one tomorrow.

25:46.540 --> 25:48.020
Know the meaning of ice crackles?

25:51.300 --> 25:52.430
Winter is over.

25:53.100 --> 25:54.190
Spring is back.

25:54.630 --> 25:55.580
It's the same for you.

25:56.430 --> 25:57.540
Nightmares are gone.

25:58.910 --> 26:00.020
Wounds will heal.

26:08.100 --> 26:09.500
I love it when you care about me.

26:10.500 --> 26:12.100
I'm afraid I can't stop myself

26:13.340 --> 26:14.390
from being weak around you.

26:16.390 --> 26:17.740
I allow you to be weak.

26:20.060 --> 26:20.900
Simu,

26:21.540 --> 26:22.710
I've always wanted to know

26:23.340 --> 26:24.470
what it was that moved you

26:25.780 --> 26:26.740
and made you accept me.

26:34.100 --> 26:34.940
What a fool.

26:36.950 --> 26:38.740
Your Grace, you're bighearted.

26:39.630 --> 26:40.470
So please tell me.

26:53.390 --> 26:54.580
(Foolish devotion.)

26:55.710 --> 26:57.190
(You're a clever man,)

26:58.020 --> 26:59.540
(but you act like a fool)

27:00.820 --> 27:02.260
(to keep me worried.)

27:15.710 --> 27:16.550
Get out of the way.

27:17.300 --> 27:18.190
That's him.

27:18.190 --> 27:19.060
Get out of the way!

27:19.190 --> 27:20.380
- Move aside!
- Move aside!

27:21.540 --> 27:22.430
All of you, move aside!

27:23.470 --> 27:24.500
How detestable.

27:24.500 --> 27:26.230
Isn't that Young Priest Luda?

27:27.820 --> 27:28.660
I heard

27:28.820 --> 27:30.150
he was deprived of his status

27:30.470 --> 27:31.740
and exiled to Youzhou.

27:31.740 --> 27:33.260
I heard he became the Young Priest

27:33.260 --> 27:34.820
because his father bred an evil spirit

27:34.820 --> 27:36.060
and sacrificed the lives

27:36.060 --> 27:36.900
of his siblings.

27:37.670 --> 27:39.500
A traitor deserves to die!

27:40.580 --> 27:41.420
Get out of the way!

27:42.260 --> 27:43.100
Move back!

27:43.820 --> 27:44.990
Back, move back!

27:44.990 --> 27:45.910
Step back.

27:45.910 --> 27:47.150
Move back now.

27:47.150 --> 27:48.340
Kill him!

27:48.340 --> 27:49.180
Just die!

27:49.390 --> 27:50.640
Hit him! Kill him!

27:50.640 --> 27:51.480
Move back.

27:51.490 --> 27:53.390
Hit him! Kill him!

27:53.910 --> 27:56.230
The world is vast.
Living beings are small.

27:57.910 --> 27:59.430
This is karma.

28:01.580 --> 28:03.100
Yet it might be reversed.

28:05.300 --> 28:06.870
Have mercy upon us.

28:10.430 --> 28:12.580
There's confusion.

28:15.230 --> 28:16.780
They're all my people.

28:19.470 --> 28:22.390
The world is vast.
Living beings are small.

28:23.340 --> 28:24.630
This is karma.

28:25.100 --> 28:26.300
Yet it might be reversed.

28:28.580 --> 28:29.990
Have mercy upon us.

28:30.500 --> 28:31.910
There's confusion.

28:34.740 --> 28:37.260
(Yuzao Pleasure House)

28:37.340 --> 28:39.150
There's a vacancy
for the Minister of War.

28:40.630 --> 28:41.780
What's Duke Pei's plan?

28:42.430 --> 28:43.670
Duke Pei

28:43.670 --> 28:45.190
wants this position

28:45.340 --> 28:46.230
to remain vacant.

28:46.630 --> 28:47.580
When things cool down,

28:47.580 --> 28:48.420
he'll decide.

28:49.100 --> 28:49.990
Who is

28:50.150 --> 28:51.150
Chancellor Du's choice,

28:51.390 --> 28:52.260
you or Meng Qiaoyan?

28:52.540 --> 28:53.630
Meng Qiaoyan, I think.

28:54.740 --> 28:55.740
According to my father,

28:56.300 --> 28:57.500
I'll be kept in the army

28:57.910 --> 28:59.020
to replace Qin Huanda.

29:00.390 --> 29:01.260
That's perfect.

29:01.260 --> 29:02.100
It's what you want.

29:04.910 --> 29:05.750
I won't be staying

29:05.750 --> 29:06.620
much longer.

29:07.950 --> 29:08.870
14 northern prefectures

29:10.060 --> 29:11.150
are waiting for us.

29:18.020 --> 29:19.950
His Majesty expanded
the horse ranch in Yunzhou.

29:20.190 --> 29:21.100
He'll certainly appoint

29:21.100 --> 29:22.580
a governor for Yunzhou and Luozhou

29:22.910 --> 29:23.990
to command all the affairs.

29:24.190 --> 29:25.030
I want

29:25.820 --> 29:26.660
this job.

29:27.630 --> 29:28.540
To recover the north,

29:28.870 --> 29:29.740
Yunzhou's horse ranch

29:29.740 --> 29:31.430
and Luozhou's mine are very important.

29:32.020 --> 29:33.340
You risked your life for them.

29:33.950 --> 29:34.870
I won't trust

29:35.260 --> 29:36.100
anyone else with it.

29:44.230 --> 29:45.070
Fang Ji,

29:45.870 --> 29:46.710
do you like Jingyuan?

29:52.390 --> 29:53.710
In the first few years I returned,

29:55.230 --> 29:56.260
Jingyuan talked to me

29:56.260 --> 29:57.470
all day long.

29:58.060 --> 29:59.150
Her praises never repeated.

29:59.870 --> 30:01.340
But she wasn't praising me,

30:01.990 --> 30:02.830
but you.

30:03.300 --> 30:04.300
If you like my sister,

30:04.740 --> 30:05.740
I believe you may

30:06.230 --> 30:07.150
make a good couple.

30:07.390 --> 30:08.670
Don't be ridiculous.

30:09.100 --> 30:10.020
Everyone knows

30:10.190 --> 30:11.430
we're mortal enemies.

30:11.950 --> 30:13.470
Besides, she'd never accept me

30:13.470 --> 30:14.910
unless you told her the truth

30:15.150 --> 30:16.390
of what happened in Daizhou.

30:17.150 --> 30:18.100
And your father.

30:18.580 --> 30:19.780
He's been hating me.

30:20.160 --> 30:21.020
There's no way

30:21.020 --> 30:22.100
he would approve of this.

30:22.260 --> 30:23.340
Quite a lot of reasons.

30:24.390 --> 30:25.670
None is that you don't like her.

30:30.950 --> 30:34.260
Close the doors and windows!
Keep out thieves!

30:37.190 --> 30:38.710
Close the doors and windows!

30:38.710 --> 30:40.580
- Shunxi, you're leaving?
- Keep out thieves!

30:41.710 --> 30:42.670
My lady

30:42.820 --> 30:44.430
painted in the yard with her hair wet.

30:44.780 --> 30:45.910
Then she caught a cold.

30:46.430 --> 30:47.500
I should take care of her.

30:47.500 --> 30:48.580
Your lady?

30:48.820 --> 30:49.660
Yes, it's her,

30:49.870 --> 30:50.710
the Sovereign.

30:50.910 --> 30:51.950
A spirit can get sick?

30:53.470 --> 30:54.670
She's special, you know.

30:58.300 --> 30:59.140
Fang Ji.

31:00.020 --> 31:01.100
I have one more

31:01.100 --> 31:01.950
lifelong wish now.

31:02.630 --> 31:04.150
To marry into her clan.

31:07.820 --> 31:08.670
We had a deal.

31:09.870 --> 31:10.710
I'll be a general,

31:11.020 --> 31:12.340
fighting wars everywhere.

31:13.020 --> 31:13.950
You'll be a chancellor,

31:14.390 --> 31:15.740
governing the court.

31:16.950 --> 31:18.150
I don't mind if I will

31:18.430 --> 31:19.270
no longer be needed.

31:21.780 --> 31:22.670
By then, I'll retire.

31:23.630 --> 31:24.910
And you'll just govern the court.

32:30.630 --> 32:31.470
Let me see.

32:39.190 --> 32:40.030
Come on.

32:41.580 --> 32:42.740
(He Simu,)

32:43.820 --> 32:46.340
(you still chose that mortal.)

32:48.470 --> 32:49.820
Come on. Wrap it tighter.

32:53.020 --> 32:53.860
I'll go get the medicine.

33:02.710 --> 33:04.710
(You're pushing me this hard)

33:05.470 --> 33:07.540
(just like everybody else.)

33:15.340 --> 33:16.260
Take it later.

33:16.710 --> 33:17.550
It's hot.

33:22.060 --> 33:23.300
Being human is really a bother.

33:24.230 --> 33:25.710
Just some wind got me sick.

33:30.780 --> 33:31.670
It's a rare experience.

33:33.150 --> 33:34.580
Sickness is part of a full life.

33:36.870 --> 33:37.710
Here.

33:42.150 --> 33:44.230
I'd rather have
fewer experiences like this.

33:45.150 --> 33:45.990
Open your mouth.

33:49.910 --> 33:51.230
I can't taste the flavor.

33:51.820 --> 33:53.060
Why did you give me this?

33:54.190 --> 33:55.030
Simu,

33:55.950 --> 33:57.190
you aren't afraid of bitterness.

33:57.990 --> 33:58.830
But I am.

34:00.060 --> 34:00.900
So?

34:02.990 --> 34:03.870
I'm going to kiss you.

34:05.190 --> 34:06.740
Restrain yourself.

34:07.060 --> 34:08.430
Do you also want to get sick?

34:15.700 --> 34:16.540
One more sip.

34:26.750 --> 34:27.590
Simu,

34:28.350 --> 34:30.180
when will you be fully recovered?

34:31.910 --> 34:32.790
Why?

34:34.830 --> 34:36.180
I should take you out for a stroll.

34:37.750 --> 34:39.620
There's a ball game in a couple of days.

34:40.620 --> 34:41.950
Do you want to watch me play?

34:45.470 --> 34:46.910
I'll ask Jingyuan to go with you.

35:23.790 --> 35:24.750
Miss He,

35:24.750 --> 35:25.950
you're the most beautiful girl

35:26.100 --> 35:27.220
in the whole place.

35:27.580 --> 35:28.420
I told you, huh?

35:28.750 --> 35:29.750
You look great in this.

35:31.060 --> 35:31.900
Let's go.

35:52.910 --> 35:54.580
The ball game in Nandu

35:54.580 --> 35:56.140
is held in spring, summer, and autumn.

35:56.700 --> 35:58.100
Since my brother started to play,

35:58.270 --> 35:59.310
he has always scored first.

35:59.660 --> 36:00.660
They had no other choice

36:00.870 --> 36:01.830
but to change the rules.

36:02.180 --> 36:04.020
One can't win
until he scores five points.

36:04.350 --> 36:06.100
My brother just played for fun.

36:06.430 --> 36:07.500
He scored once and exited.

36:08.700 --> 36:09.750
But he said

36:10.060 --> 36:11.140
he'd play the full match.

36:11.500 --> 36:12.340
Miss He,

36:12.350 --> 36:13.270
you just wait and see.

36:18.320 --> 36:19.180
Look.

36:19.180 --> 36:20.540
That man is so handsome.

36:20.540 --> 36:21.390
Mr. Duan.

36:21.400 --> 36:22.700
That's Duan Xu.

36:23.140 --> 36:24.020
Look.

36:25.540 --> 36:26.660
He's charming.

36:27.140 --> 36:28.580
He scores first every time.

36:28.580 --> 36:29.420
Xu!

36:29.990 --> 36:30.830
Meng.

36:44.470 --> 36:45.310
Duan Shunxi?

36:46.990 --> 36:48.830
A few days ago, you had a big problem

36:48.830 --> 36:49.670
and stayed indoors.

36:49.950 --> 36:51.060
We all thought

36:51.060 --> 36:52.270
you were so depressed

36:52.270 --> 36:53.620
that you would quit.

36:53.950 --> 36:54.790
Yeah.

36:55.020 --> 36:55.860
That's right.

36:56.750 --> 36:58.140
Then why are you still in the mood

36:58.470 --> 36:59.430
for this game?

37:00.430 --> 37:01.350
Staying depressed

37:01.350 --> 37:02.190
won't solve anything.

37:02.910 --> 37:03.830
Today I'll see the ball

37:03.830 --> 37:04.790
as the Chong enemy.

37:05.060 --> 37:07.660
I'll vent my displeasure on the court.

37:10.470 --> 37:11.700
So, I'll play the full match.

37:12.620 --> 37:14.100
Gentlemen, no hard feelings.

37:14.100 --> 37:15.990
- Full match?
- Full?

37:16.540 --> 37:17.620
Only Meng Wan and Qingsheng

37:17.620 --> 37:18.460
will be on my team.

37:18.910 --> 37:20.020
You make up your own teams.

37:20.750 --> 37:22.140
Can't you corner and stop

37:22.140 --> 37:22.980
only the three of us?

37:24.150 --> 37:24.990
- Fine.
- All right.

37:24.990 --> 37:25.870
That'd be perfect.

37:25.870 --> 37:27.010
- Yeah.
- All right.

37:41.290 --> 37:42.140
How come Xu's team

37:42.140 --> 37:43.140
only has three people?

37:43.660 --> 37:45.180
Are they bullying him?

37:46.700 --> 37:48.350
Who could possibly bully him?

37:51.990 --> 37:52.830
That's right.

38:00.270 --> 38:01.390
I've been repressed so much.

38:01.950 --> 38:04.350
Today, I'll have enough fun!

38:23.870 --> 38:24.710
Miss He!

38:25.100 --> 38:26.580
My brother scored first!

38:27.220 --> 38:28.270
- Xu!
- Hurry.

38:28.270 --> 38:29.140
Xu!

38:29.140 --> 38:29.980
Stop him!

38:37.420 --> 38:38.270
Quickly!

38:38.270 --> 38:39.620
Honey, let's go closer and watch.

38:39.620 --> 38:40.470
All right. Let's go.

38:40.470 --> 38:41.310
Stop him.

38:41.310 --> 38:42.150
Block him.

38:43.180 --> 38:44.020
Miss He,

38:44.020 --> 38:45.140
let's get down there too.

38:45.140 --> 38:46.500
You can shout as loud as you want.

38:46.500 --> 38:47.340
You'll enjoy it.

38:48.330 --> 38:49.180
I don't want to shout.

38:49.180 --> 38:50.350
How could you not want that?

38:50.350 --> 38:51.660
You'll want to shout by then.

38:51.670 --> 38:52.540
Come on. Let's go.

38:52.540 --> 38:53.380
Come on.

38:53.830 --> 38:54.670
Hurry.

38:55.580 --> 38:56.420
Honey, look.

38:56.580 --> 38:57.420
Stop him.

38:58.340 --> 38:59.180
Mr. Duan

38:59.180 --> 39:00.220
plays so well.

39:04.910 --> 39:05.750
Bravo!

39:05.810 --> 39:06.660
Xu,

39:06.660 --> 39:07.500
beat them!

39:07.500 --> 39:08.360
He's going to score.

39:08.360 --> 39:09.830
Beat them!

39:25.990 --> 39:26.990
Bravo!

39:27.700 --> 39:28.700
Nice!

39:29.060 --> 39:29.990
Impressive!

39:30.180 --> 39:31.470
Xu!

39:31.990 --> 39:38.910
First score! First score!

40:04.240 --> 40:09.570
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

40:09.900 --> 40:14.150
♪Light encountered shadow♪

40:15.510 --> 40:20.880
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

40:21.180 --> 40:25.780
♪The unbreakable fate♪

40:26.870 --> 40:28.710
♪Suddenly cracked♪

40:40.920 --> 40:46.360
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

40:46.540 --> 40:50.870
♪Light encountered shadow♪

40:52.240 --> 40:57.630
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

40:57.860 --> 41:01.800
♪The unbreakable fate♪

41:03.570 --> 41:05.460
♪Suddenly cracked♪

41:08.120 --> 41:11.280
♪Listen, all sounds are roaring♪

41:11.280 --> 41:13.810
♪As cold ice turns into tides♪

41:13.810 --> 41:19.330
♪A century's loneliness melts dreams♪

41:19.330 --> 41:22.570
♪Following fate's guidance♪

41:22.570 --> 41:27.430
♪By fate, our moments were exchanged♪

41:27.770 --> 41:30.790
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪

41:30.790 --> 41:33.610
♪Watch fireworks fall like stars♪

41:33.870 --> 41:36.400
♪This bond is tangled into a thread♪

41:36.400 --> 41:41.820
♪Worldly reflections fade into mist♪

41:41.990 --> 41:45.060
♪Borrowing one fleeting heartbeat♪

41:45.220 --> 41:50.120
♪You drew me into mortal dust,
till I'm enamored with its charms♪

41:50.330 --> 41:53.800
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪
